<div id="review_1630513556" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1630513556" />
    <a title="Zoeytron" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/12656534-zoeytron"><img alt="Zoeytron" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1542977636p2/12656534.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1630513556?book_show_action=true">May 10, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Zoeytron" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Zoeytron" href="/user/show/12656534-zoeytron">Zoeytron</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780316252034" href="/book/show/25674405-life-or-death">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12656534-zoeytron?shelf=public-library">public-library</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1630513556" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9603571156455652252">Expectations.  They can be dashed to smithereens by one poor decision.  Audie Spencer Palmer, with only one day left of his 10 year prison sentence, escapes under the cover of night.  Makes no sense, does it?  Oh, but Audie has his reasons.  And he has a plan.  Tuck into this thriller after you have done your chores, as you will not want to roust yourself after you start reading.  Terrific characters and a great story!  </span>

          </span>
        </div>


