              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13624759802735614694">Wow! This is the first book that I have read by this author and I will certainly be reading more. I don&apos;t want to say too much as I am afraid of giving something away but I tore through this book in two days. I did not want to put it down.<br/>Audie is serving a 10 year prison sentence for the robbery of an armoured van containing 7 million dollars, the murder of four people and an accident that killed an unidentified woman. Over the years of his sentence everyone has tried to get the location of the</span>
  <span id="freeText13624759802735614694" style="display:none">Wow! This is the first book that I have read by this author and I will certainly be reading more. I don't want to say too much as I am afraid of giving something away but I tore through this book in two days. I did not want to put it down.<br />Audie is serving a 10 year prison sentence for the robbery of an armoured van containing 7 million dollars, the murder of four people and an accident that killed an unidentified woman. Over the years of his sentence everyone has tried to get the location of the money out of Audie. <br />Audie escapes the day before he is due to be released and everyone is puzzled by this. The story in its entirety unfolds and I was holding my breath for about the last 20 pages.<br />A brilliant story that I highly recommend.</span>
