        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1351101302" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer454028460165217522">I love this author and this was a good story but IMHO not up there with his other books I have enjoyed. A man breaks out of prison the day before he is to be released after serving an unblemished 10 year term, for a 7 million dollar robbery. I liked the main character but some of the plot was a bit far fetched. A buddy read with my very good book buddy Mary Beth. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


